Template: stargus/extractdata
Type: boolean
Default: true
_Description: Extract Starcraft data files now?
 Stargus needs data files from original Starcraft CD.

Template: stargus/cdpath
Type: string
Default: /media/cdrom
_Description: Starcraft CD mount point:
 Enter path to your Starcraft CD mount point

Template: stargus/nodata
Type: error
_Description: Data files not found
 Starcraft CD was not found in specified path. Specify another
 path which contains correct Starcraft data files.
